  <brief_title>BDP/FF Versus Formoterol Fumarate (FF) in Patients With Severe COPD (Lung Function and Exacerbation Rate)</brief_title>
  <official_title>a 48-week, Double Blind, Randomized, Multinational, Multicentre, &quot;Fixed Combination&quot; Beclomethasone Dipropionate Plus Formoterol Fumarate Versus Formoterol in Patients With Severe Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease</official_title>
  <sponsors>
