  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      a 48-week, 2-arm parallel group, &quot;fixed combination&quot; beclomethasone dipropionate plus
      formoterol fumarate versus formoterol in patients with severe chronic obstructive pulmonary
      disease
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      a 48-week, double blind, randomized, multinational, multicentre, 2-arm parallel group,
      reference treatment controlled clinical trial of &quot;fixed combination&quot; beclomethasone
      dipropionate plus formoterol fumarate versus formoterol in patients with severe chronic
      obstructive pulmonary disease
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
